"Search for phrase \"foo bar\" in the post title field AND the phrase \"quick "
"fox\" in the post content field."
msgstr ""
"Cerca la frase \"foo bar\" nel campo titolo del post e la frase \"quick fox"
"\" nel campo contenuto del post."

#: admin/cloud-search-admin-docs.php:311
msgid ""
"Search for either the phrase \"foo bar\" in the post title field AND the "
