#: admin/cloud-search-admin-docs.php:321
msgid ""
"Search for any word that starts with \"foo\" and ends with \"bar\" in the "
"post title field."
msgstr ""
"Cerca qualsiasi parola che inizia con \"foo\" e che  termina con \"bar\" nel "
"campo titolo del post."

#: admin/cloud-search-admin-docs.php:322
msgid ""
"Note that Lucene does not support using a * symbol as the first character of "
