#: admin/cloud-search-admin-docs.php:607
msgid ""
"In the \"Setting\" section you have the opportunity to customize the \"no "
"results\" message using a simple string, but you can also set an HTML "
"template if you want to highly customize the \"no results\" message. If you "
"are using a custom template none text messages will be displayed and if your "
