"box type in the \"Frontpage settings\", you can create your search page and "
"choose to not use the built-in search page using for example a different "
"Javascript library (e.g. AngularJS or other frameworks instead of jQuery). "
"These operations are suggested if you are using a custom theme and if you "
"want to show more details or if you want a \"not-standard\" behavior in the "
"result boxes."
msgstr ""
